	    var mapInitialized = false;

	    function showHideMap() {
	        if (mapDisplayed) {
	            $("#map_parent").fadeOut();
	            mapDisplayed = false;
	            $("#map_link").html("Map these results");
	        }
	        else {
	            $("#map_parent").fadeIn();

	    function getMapLink(id) {
	    	var cb = Math.round(new Date().getTime());

	    	var url = $("#lnkMap1-" + id).attr("wizzy");

	    	if (typeof url == 'undefined') {
	    		$.ajax({
	    			url: "/members/MapMember.aspx?CdbID=" + id + "&cb=" + cb,
	    			async: false,
	    			dataType: 'json',
	    			success: function(json) {
	    				getMapLinkSuccess(json, id);
	    			},
	    			complete: function() {
	    				return false;
	    			}
	    		});
	    	}
	    	else {
	    		if (url == "0") {
	    			NoAccess();
	    		}
	    		else {
	    			showMap(url);
	    		}
	    	}
	    }

	    function showMap(url) {
	    	openPopup(url, 'MapSearch', 'toolbar=false,scrollbars,resizable', 900, 650);
	    }
		
	    function getMapLinkSuccess(data, cdbid) {
	    	if (data.ok && data.ok == "true") {
	    		$("#lnkMap1-" + cdbid).attr("wizzy", data.url);
	    		$("#lnkMap2-" + cdbid).attr("wizzy", data.url);
	    		showMap(data.url);
	    	}
	    	else {
	    		$("#lnkMap1-" + cdbid).attr("wizzy", "0");
	    		$("#lnkMap2-" + cdbid).attr("wizzy", "0");
	    		NoAccess();
	    	}
		}

	    function NoAccess() {
	    	window.alert("You do not have access to this member's profile.");
	    }

	</script>

			<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
				YAHOO.namespace("container");

				function YAHOOinitConnectionRequestForm(){
					YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm =
						new YAHOO.widget.Panel("ConnectionRequestFormPanel", { width: '350px',
							underlay: 'shadow',
							close: true,
							visible: false,
							draggable: false
						});
						YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm.render();
                        $('#ConnectionRequestFormPanel_c').css('z-index', 100);
						initCxDiagDefaults();
				}

				YAHOO.util.Event.onDOMReady(YAHOOinitConnectionRequestForm);

				function initCxDiagDefaults() {
					$(".YmDefaultValue").each(function() {
						if ($(this).val() != $(this).attr('DefaultValue')) {
							$(this).removeClass('DefaultValue');
							$(this).addClass('deemphasize');
						}
					});

					$(".YmDefaultValue").focus(function() {
						if ($(this).val() == $(this).attr('DefaultValue')) {
							$(this).val('');
							$(this).removeClass('DefaultValue');
							$(this).removeClass('deemphasize');
						}
					});

					$(".YmDefaultValue").blur(function() {
						if ($(this).val().length == 0) {
							$(this).val($(this).attr('DefaultValue'));
							$(this).addClass('DefaultValue');
							$(this).addClass('deemphasize');
						}
					});
				}

				function ShowConnectionRequestForm2(CdbID1, CdbID2, FriendlyName, ContextID) {
					ShowConnectionRequestForm3(CdbID1, CdbID2, FriendlyName, ContextID, "tr", "br");
				}

				function ShowConnectionRequestForm3(CdbID1, CdbID2, FriendlyName, ContextID, DiagCorner, ContextCorner) {
					YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm.cfg.setProperty("context", [ContextID, DiagCorner, ContextCorner, ["beforeShow", "windowResize"]]);
					ShowConnectionRequestForm(CdbID1, CdbID2, FriendlyName);
				}

				function ShowConnectionRequestForm(CdbID1, CdbID2, FriendlyName) {
					//Reset a few things
					$("#ConnectionRequestWrapper").show();
					$("#ConnectionRequestError").html('');
					$("#ConnectionRequestStatus").html('');
					$("#txtConnReqMsg").show();
					$("#ConnectionRequestBtns").show();
					$("#ConnectionRequestButton").show();
					$("#ConnectionRequestButton").removeAttr('disabled');

					//Set new values
					$("#hidCdbID1").val(CdbID1);
					$("#hidCdbID2").val(CdbID2);
					$("#ConnectionRequestTargetName").html(FriendlyName);
					
					CheckIsConnected();
				}

				function HideConnectionRequestForm() {
					//IE hack: underlay size does not change with panel size; resize it now
					if (document.all) YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm.sizeUnderlay();
					YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm.hide();
				}

				function handleConnectionRequestResponse(data) {
					if (data)  {
						if (data.status) {
							$('#ConnectionRequestStatus').html('Connection request has been sent!<br/><br/><a href="javascript:HideConnectionRequestForm();">Close this window</a>');
							$("#txtConnReqMsg").val('');							
							$('#ConnectionRequestWrapper').hide();
							if (document.all) YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm.sizeUnderlay();
						}
						else {
							$('#ConnectionRequestError').html(data.errormsg);
							$('#ConnectionRequestButton').removeAttr('disabled');
						}
					}
					$("#ConnectionRequestWorking").hide();
				}

				function SendConnectionRequest() {
					var cdbid1 = $("#hidCdbID1").val();
					var cdbid2 = $("#hidCdbID2").val();
					var clientid = $("#hidClientAppID").val();
					var msg = $("#txtConnReqMsg").val();
					msg = replaceReturns(stripHtml(msg));
					$("#ConnectionRequestWorking").show();
					$('#ConnectionRequestButton').attr('disabled', 'disabled');
					$.ajax({
						url: '/global_engine/ajax/ConnectionRequest.aspx',
						data: 'CdbID=' + cdbid1 + '&CDbID2=' + cdbid2 + '&message=' + msg + '&cb=' + Math.round(new Date().getTime()),
						dataType: 'json',
						success: function(data) { handleConnectionRequestResponse(data); },
						error: function(xhr,msg) { $("#ConnectionRequestWorking").hide(); $('#ConnectionRequestError').html('Unable to process connection request. ' + msg); $('#ConnectionRequestButton').removeAttr('disabled'); }
					});
				}

				function handleIsConnectedResponse(data) {
					var canConnect = true;
					var msg = 'You may already be connected or have a pending connection request.';

					if (data) {
						if (data.isconnected) {
							canConnect = false;
							msg = 'You are already connected to this member.';
						}

						if (data.ispending) {
							canConnect = false;
							msg = 'Your connection with this member is pending.';
						}

						if (!data.mtallowed) {
							canConnect = false;
							msg = 'You are not allowed to connect to members of this type.';
						}
					}
					if (canConnect) {
						$("#ConnectionRequestWrapper").show();
					}
					else {
						//Either already connected or an error occured.
						$("#ConnectionRequestWrapper").hide();
						$('#ConnectionRequestError').html(msg + '<br/><br/><a href="javascript:HideConnectionRequestForm();">Close this window</a>');
					}

					//IE hack: underlay size does not change with panel size; resize it now
					if (document.all) YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm.sizeUnderlay();

					YAHOO.container.ConnectionRequestForm.show();

					//Focus Daniel-san
					//window.setTimeout('$("#ConnectionRequestButton").focus();', 200);
					window.setTimeout('$("#txtConnReqMsg").blur();', 200);
				}

				function CheckIsConnected() {
					var cdbid1 = $("#hidCdbID1").val();
					var cdbid2 = $("#hidCdbID2").val();

					$.ajax({
						url: '/global_engine/ajax/ConnectionRequest.aspx',
						data: 'CdbID=' + cdbid1 + '&CDbID2=' + cdbid2 + '&IsConnected=true&cb=' + Math.round(new Date().getTime()),
						dataType: 'json',
						success: function(data) { handleIsConnectedResponse(data); },
						error: function(xhr,msg) { handleIsConnectedResponse(null); }
					});
				}
			</script>
